>\n<br />\n係唔想去整頭既人仲on 尻尻以為自己用緊純天然</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家有咩係天然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2904be86cf3d99e8328664e43be67829ecae46","tid":27364,"uid":53046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來炒左樓主 = 無人性<br />\n<br />\n炒廢柴唔撚得？<br />\n<br />\n你幫到老細賺錢既話又會炒你？<br />\n<br />\n弱智抵撚死你比人炒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講左佢炒我唔緊要<br />\n您有冇睇內容？我後生搵過份有幾唔閒<br />\n係佢講既同做既唔同<br />\n純天然？咩叫純天然？話自己100%天然<br />\n但係想溝野落染髮濟握啲客 咁都叫有人性？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你點解唔告去銷委會？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想丫 佢張商業登記證都過哂期<br />\n問佢佢話有張新既 不過冇帶番黎<br />\n係咪好有問題先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣已經夠玩死佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望您明白 我唔係唔鋸比人炒 我都話我咁後生 打佢份工老老實實萬零蚊個月 我比佢炒我周圍都搵到份差唔多人工既 我唔鋸係佢連人地啊姐掃地 佢都炒埋 仲要諗住握消費者"},{"pid":"4796757a423525b17fae8c4d54126088bda8d1d7","tid":27364,"uid":53046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>炒你實有原因  好好反省下啦  <br />\n仲上網玩公審</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係唔想去整頭既人仲on 尻尻以為自己用緊純天然</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家有咩係天然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係天然唔緊要 但係您唔好握尻啲消費者話係純天然<br />\n人地有cancer 信您係統天然 跟住個個月黎整 咁樣係唔係好冇人性？有cancer 黎整頭我見唔少 做乜要咁樣害人？"},{"pid":"d977e7039bf5b94415cb0bd74f0e1b96be0d02d9","tid":27364,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"明明佢周身屎 玩佢容乜易"},{"pid":"5288bfbb662d4754bbbde53d39a3416eb3de7556","tid":27364,"uid":53046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明佢周身屎 玩佢容乜易</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係聽佢死 我只係唔想再有人比佢握<br />\n錢係其次 人地身體有事個啲點算好？"},{"pid":"2ac162af611e7645de051751b299b518928cf7e2","tid":27364,"uid":16451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"咁都係黑店姐 <br />\n無良僱主？年紀大唔炒得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16081d4d2d994e670f01bde7bdc03aa9a6e88e16","tid":27364,"uid":23272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"樓主分分鐘要搵定律師"},{"pid":"136e5f4305df628037a398be4aac18f715fbac3a","tid":27364,"uid":53046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都係黑店姐 <br />\n無良僱主？年紀大唔炒得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人無良 再加佢係僱主 咁係唔係無良僱主？<br />\n你老母你咪撚捉字塞啦係到<br />\n你試下生cancer 去整頭 一心諗住純天然<br />\n後來發覺比人握 您又會點撚樣？<br />\n懶係型咁入黎捉字塞 番屋企訓陣先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80b5d1ab5f85a45511846807b2c7caa1a206d9c","tid":27364,"uid":28608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁都係黑店姐 <br />\n無良僱主？年紀大唔炒得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人無良 再加佢係僱主 咁係唔係無良僱主？<br />\n你老母你咪撚捉字塞啦係到<br />\n你試下生cancer 去整頭 一心諗住純天然<br />\n後來發覺比人握 您又會點撚樣？<br />\n懶係型咁入黎捉字塞 番屋企訓陣先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生cancer係都做化癒先，仲整頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不如話和尚去整頭<br />\n仲有染得髮既人都唔撚天然嫁啦，唔係乜叫天然髮色，名黎姐，唔通菠蘿包有菠<br />\n睇你咁on9,炒你係有原因"},{"pid":"2c77fae2b417818fd60e81aa10b54356d69f2861","tid":27364,"uid":53046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-